e to righteous character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, my prayer, my rites, my life, and my death are for Allah the Lord of the worlds. He has no partner and with this I have been commanded and I am among the Muslims.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24280,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/funeral-good-witness\/","url_meta":{"origin":34932,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Muslims whose good is witnessed enter Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhenever four persons testify to the goodness of a Muslim, he will enter Paradise.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd three?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven three.\u201d We said, \u201cAnd two?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cEven two.\u201d Thereafter, we did not ask\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/29\/dhikr-better-than-jihad-qital\/","url_meta":{"origin":34932,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Remembering Allah even better than jihad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShall I not tell you of the best of your deeds, which is the purest to your King, which raises you among your ranks, which is better for you than spending gold and money in charity, and which\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":16880,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/10\/30\/forgive-or-be-like-him\/","url_meta":{"origin":34932,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Forgiveness: Pardon the murderer, or be like him","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 30, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, with the killer of his relative. The Prophet said, \u201cPardon him,\u201d but the man refused. The Prophet said, \u201cTake the blood money,\u201d but the man refused. The Prophet said, \u201cGo and kill\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34932","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments